headline: Walgreens Committed to Supporting Rite Aid Customers and Employees
summary: DEERFIELD, Ill., May 09, 2025--In light of Rite Aid's recent bankruptcy filing, Walgreens is committed to assisting Rite Aid customers and employees who are impacted by store closures in their local community.
